### =========================================================
### AEM EDS Admin API — wknd-backlink-test
### =========================================================
### Use with VS Code "REST Client" extension or IntelliJ HTTP client
### Preview = .aem.page (draft) | Live = .aem.live (production)
### Content source: Google Drive
### =========================================================
###
### SETUP STEPS (one-time):
###
###   1. Create a GitHub repo with AEM EDS boilerplate code
###      - fstab.yaml should point to your Google Drive folder:
###        mountpoints:
###          /: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/{folderId}
###
###   2. Install AEM Code Sync on the repo
###      - Go to: https://github.com/apps/aem-code-sync/installations/new
###      - Select your account, add the repo, click Install
###
###   3. Share your Google Drive folder with helix@adobe.com (editor)
###
###   4. Make sure your Drive folder has content
###      - At minimum: index (Google Doc), nav, footer
###      - For redirects: a Google Sheet named redirects
###
###   5. Run the /code endpoint below to sync your repo config
###
###   6. Run the /preview endpoint to fetch content from Google Drive
###
###   7. Check /status — sourceLocation should show gdrive:
###
###   8. Open the preview URL in your browser to verify:
###      https://main--wknd-backlink-test--mimchome.aem.page/
###
### =========================================================

@base = https://admin.hlx.page
@org = mimchome
@repo = wknd-backlink-test
@branch = main
@site = {{org}}/{{repo}}/{{branch}}


### =========================================================
### CODE UPDATE (POST — forces EDS to re-read fstab.yaml)
### =========================================================
### Run this after changing fstab.yaml or any repo config.

### Refresh code/config
POST {{base}}/code/{{site}}/


### =========================================================
### PREVIEW (POST → .aem.page)
### =========================================================

### Preview home
POST {{base}}/preview/{{site}}/

### Preview trips
POST {{base}}/preview/{{site}}/trips

### Preview nav
POST {{base}}/preview/{{site}}/nav

### Preview footer
POST {{base}}/preview/{{site}}/footer

### Preview redirects sheet (.json suffix for Sheets)
POST {{base}}/preview/{{site}}/redirects.json


### =========================================================
### PUBLISH (POST → .aem.live)
### =========================================================

### Publish home
POST {{base}}/live/{{site}}/

### Publish trips
POST {{base}}/live/{{site}}/trips

### Publish nav
POST {{base}}/live/{{site}}/nav

### Publish footer
POST {{base}}/live/{{site}}/footer

### Publish redirects sheet
POST {{base}}/live/{{site}}/redirects.json


### =========================================================
### STATUS (GET)
### =========================================================

### Status home
GET {{base}}/status/{{site}}/

### Status trips
GET {{base}}/status/{{site}}/trips

### Status redirects
GET {{base}}/status/{{site}}/redirects.json


### =========================================================
### UNPUBLISH (DELETE — clears CDN cache)
### =========================================================

### Unpublish adventures from live
DELETE {{base}}/live/{{site}}/adventures

### Unpublish adventures from preview
DELETE {{base}}/preview/{{site}}/adventures


### =========================================================
### PREVIEW URL (open in browser to verify)
### =========================================================
###
### https://main--wknd-backlink-test--mimchome.aem.page/


### =========================================================
### GOOGLE SHEETS API — Manage redirects sheet
### =========================================================
###
### SETUP (one-time):
###   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
###   2. Create a project (or use existing)
###   3. Enable "Google Sheets API" under APIs & Services
###   4. Create OAuth 2.0 credentials (type: Web application)
###      - Add redirect URI: https://oauth.pgltools.com/callback (for REST Client)
###      - Or: https://developers.google.com/oauthplayground (for playground)
###   5. Copy Client ID and Client Secret below
###
### GET YOUR SPREADSHEET ID:
###   Open your redirects sheet → URL looks like:
###   https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/XXXXX/edit
###   The XXXXX part is your sheetId

@sheetsBase = https://sheets.googleapis.com/v4/spreadsheets
@sheetId = PASTE_YOUR_SHEET_ID_HERE
@clientId = PASTE_YOUR_CLIENT_ID_HERE
@clientSecret = PASTE_YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET_HERE
@redirectUri = https://developers.google.com/oauthplayground
@authCode = PASTE_AUTH_CODE_HERE
@token = PASTE_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = PASTE_YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE


### ---- STEP 1: Get auth code (open this URL in browser) ----
### Copy this URL into your browser, sign in, authorize, copy the code from the redirect:
### https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/v2/auth?client_id={{clientId}}&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}&response_type=code&scope=https://www.googleapis.com/auth/spreadsheets&access_type=offline

### ---- STEP 2: Exchange auth code for tokens ----
### Run this ONCE after getting the auth code from step 1
### Copy access_token and refresh_token from the response into the variables above
# @name getTokens
POST https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

code={{authCode}}&client_id={{clientId}}&client_secret={{clientSecret}}&redirect_uri={{redirectUri}}&grant_type=authorization_code

### ---- STEP 3: Refresh token (when access token expires after 1hr) ----
### Use this to get a new access_token without re-authorizing
# @name refreshToken
POST https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

refresh_token={{refreshToken}}&client_id={{clientId}}&client_secret={{clientSecret}}&grant_type=refresh_token

### ---- SHEETS API CALLS ----

### Read all redirects
GET {{sheetsBase}}/{{sheetId}}/values/Sheet1!A:B
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Append a new redirect row
POST {{sheetsBase}}/{{sheetId}}/values/Sheet1!A:B:append?valueInputOption=RAW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"values": [["/old-path", "/new-path"]]}

### Append multiple redirect rows at once
POST {{sheetsBase}}/{{sheetId}}/values/Sheet1!A:B:append?valueInputOption=RAW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"values": [["/page-one", "/new-one"], ["/page-two", "/new-two"]]}

### Update a specific row (e.g. row 2)
PUT {{sheetsBase}}/{{sheetId}}/values/Sheet1!A2:B2?valueInputOption=RAW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"values": [["/magazine", "/faqs"]]}

### Clear a specific row (e.g. remove row 3)
POST {{sheetsBase}}/{{sheetId}}/values/Sheet1!A3:B3:clear
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Get sheet metadata (see sheet names, row counts)
GET {{sheetsBase}}/{{sheetId}}?fields=sheets.properties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
